"this field is left blank, that indicates the vehicle is currently available, "
"and can be reassigned to another driver. If it is populated, the vehicle is "
"not available for another driver until the selected date."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: select the company from the drop-down menu. This field "
"only appears in a multi-company database."
msgstr ""

